sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant Filter as JwtAuthFilter
    participant BC as BugController
    participant BS as BugService
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>FE: Fill bug form (title, text, tags), submit
    FE->>BC: POST /api/bugs { title, text, imageUrl }\n Authorization: Bearer JWT
    Filter->>Filter: Extract username from JWT
    Filter->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE username=?
    DB-->>Filter: User row
    Filter->>Filter: Check not banned, set SecurityContext
    BC->>BC: resolveAuthenticatedUser(auth)
    BC->>BS: createBug(BugRequest, userId)
    BS->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE id=?
    DB-->>BS: User entity
    BS->>DB: INSERT INTO bugs (title, text, status=OPEN, author_id)
    DB-->>BS: Saved Bug
    BS-->>BC: Bug entity
    BC-->>FE: 201 BugResponse { id, title, status:"OPEN", ... }
    FE->>FE: Add tags if provided
    FE->>BC: POST /api/bugs/{id}/tags ["tag1","tag2"]
    BC->>BS: addTagsToBug(bugId, tagNames)
    BS->>DB: SELECT * FROM tags WHERE name=? (per tag)
    BS->>DB: INSERT INTO tags if not exists
    BS->>DB: INSERT INTO bug_tags (bug_id, tag_id)
    DB-->>BS: Updated Bug
    BS-->>BC: Bug entity
    BC-->>FE: 200 BugResponse { ..., tags: ["tag1","tag2"] }
    FE-->>User: Bug appears in list
